description:
In part-2 of our chats with Bravo stars, some iconic Bravolebrities call in (interviews were conducted the week of March 15) to talk about their shows, what they're doing while indoors, and much more!


Kate Chastain (Below Deck): 4:10ish

Patricia Altschul (Southern Charm): 18:40ish

Braunwyn (Real Housewives of Orange County): 32:39ish

Scheana Shay (Vanderpump Rules): 41:00ish


For tickets to the Chicago live show: https://bit.ly/3bc6QLX
